" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有D類似生蠔咁既海鮮味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己仲買咗D芋頭貢丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD芋頭好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條氣管好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講有個WEME觀塘飲食谷已經超過3000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠邀大家一齊加入分享觀塘區美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%B01&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e8721661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1</a><br />\n入谷入谷,永不為奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65619fdafd9e5ca170ba28bad0fafcd6928f3aae","tid":2317023,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"師"},{"pid":"a7ff49d0cc7df1763cc2d038769a3efc6b9abcea","tid":2317023,"uid":8542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5d4a3a4d9cdb6e33563fc97e2d844edad47261","tid":2317023,"uid":129695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee8b1a17e3ba694c91c4a15cffc8ad1c67f5e50","tid":2317023,"uid":224277,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"早食師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3184568e636409587b62eece9fb74571a3c6e37d","tid":2317023,"uid":101507,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"C伏C<img