正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條氣管好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講有個WEME觀塘飲食谷已經超過3000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠邀大家一齊加入分享觀塘區美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%B01&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e8721661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1</a><br />\n入谷入谷,永不為奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"好早放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f62bd7653611bfad9628f2a32f2444d659cb88","tid":2317023,"uid":6890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"印仔成日食咁多肥野會唔會好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0789aa0f8f8eb769e75b97c547f006c6bf26b990","tid":2317023,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1aea1368cee4948acfc32bb6b7d817997dae6fc","tid":2317023,"uid":114211,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"晚餐竟然咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打手post fced<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"自費架屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d167097932a422ce9df8298adb1c8386746c30e9","tid":2317023,"uid":365380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"咁早就食晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces